<template>
  <v-app>
    <v-main></v-main>
  </v-app>
</template>

<script>
import store from "./store";

export default {
  name: "App",
  components: {},
  created() {
    store.dispatch("updateUser", {
      user: this.$cookies.get("user"),
      password: this.$cookies.get("password"),
      isAuthenticated: this.$cookies.get("isAuthenticated"),
    });
  },
};
</script>
<style></style>
